          <div class="opacity-0 transform translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out" data-lazy-animate style="animation-delay: 200ms">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">SaaS Solutions</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
              We develop comprehensive SaaS platforms that provide value to users while generating sustainable recurring revenue. Our solutions are built for scale, security, and user experience.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Multi-tenant Architecture
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Subscription Management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Payment Integration
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Analytics & Reporting
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="opacity-0 transform translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out" data-lazy-animate style="animation-delay: 400ms">
            <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Key Features</h3>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Core Features</h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                    <li>• User Management</li>
                    <li>• Role-based Access</li>
                    <li>• API Integration</li>
                    <li>• Real-time Updates</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4">
