              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Multi-tenant Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Scalable architecture that supports multiple customers with data isolation and security.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li>• Data Isolation</li>
              <li>• Resource Sharing</li>
              <li>• Custom Branding</li>
              <li>• Scalable Infrastructure</li>
            </ul>
